The Cocoa tree grows tall and slender having few limbs if any, but the leaf is from a foot or so, to 6,8,10,12, even 14 ft or more feet in length. about a foot broad or so Their are about 30 sail-ships here in the dock, only fur or five <unclear/> ships. At present The Trans-port-Sen-a-tor. 
started from Frisco when we did but we come here two hours ahead She last one soldier on the way he fell over-board when drugs or sea sick but no one saw him disappear. it was soon after they left The Golden Gate. wish to call notice to the above name and place in another letter. 